                                <h3 class="title">Participation Form</h3>
                                <b class="fserif">FIGHT CLUB PARTICIPANTS</b><br><br>
                                The class series is limited to 5-8 participants. We welcome individuals who identify as queer, disabled, or are currently on a personal healing journey to participate and join the Fight Club. To register, please fill out the form, which would ask to fill the following information:<br><br>
                                <ol class="list-number">
                                    <li>A self-introduction, explaining why you wish to participate in the Fight Club;</li>
                                    <li>A reflection or insight from your healing journey that you are willing to share with other participants;</li>
