                                <b class="fserif">A. Offline Wiki as its infromationa distribution method</b><br><br>
                                <p>
                                    TT starts Offline Wiki in 2022. The project then became the foundation for BOTAMEVE's USB stick distribution system. Offline Wiki was developed in response to various forms of censorship and internet attacks worldwide, including:
                                </p>
                                <ul class="list-dots">
                                    <li>The Chinese government's cultural erasure of Uyghurs</li>
                                    <li>Internet censorship in the Philippines</li>
                                    <li>Cuba's offline information distribution system known as "<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/El_Paquete_Semanal" target="_blank">El Paquete Semanal</a>"</li>
